{"id":511143,"date":[{"year":1971,"month":7,"day":4}],"page":"6","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"庆祝中国共产党诞生五十周年征文选刊,党的光辉照千秋","genre":"","count":"173","ytitle":"","mtitle":"红太阳照钢城","ftitle":"","authors":["鲍道佐"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"上钢一厂　鲍道佐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浦江奔腾迎朝阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十里钢城披红妆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席视察咱钢厂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万座高炉泻金浪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驰骋征途十三年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀劈腐恶豪情壮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炼一身铁骨顶天地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铸一颗红心永向阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自力更生红旗扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁流滚滚赛长江。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢锭堆得如山高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金色大道万里长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢城虎将心坦荡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捧出钢出送八方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满天钢花献给党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧跟毛主席向前闯。"}]}